      "comment": "DIMORA STRIPEY (4) jumped cleanly from the rails to lead much the way when second (22.40) at this track in a Bottom Up - Grade 6 over 390m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Can find winning form. MAJOR JEALOUS (8) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, most recently finishing 2nd at Mt Gambier over 305m. Expecting another good run. HOPE JUAN (5) struggled in tougher grade last start after drifting back at Warragul, but prior to that won by 2.5 lengths at Warragul (22.99) beating Mila's Hand in a Rank Limit - Restricted Win on June 11. Key runner on best form. WHIPSTICK JORDAN (2) is worth some thought after placing last start.",
